{"tid":2037283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得今朝冇時間冇地點冇行動指南而屌曬鬼既你入黎","createTime":"2020-05-27T01:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T02:50:22.000Z","uid":81236,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c69f215fdaee65e4a3a73205c5e0fb0c1bb8aeb","tid":2037283,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:48:01.000Z","msg":"首先以下內容唔係比想被罷工唔成但又會屌曬鬼既你睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩冇一早set時間地點救返唔少人<br />\n<br />\n首先經過上年黎明行動，佢地一早已經部署哂係所有可能被堵/塞既地點，所有分區可能集合地點都有線眼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">冇時間地點搞到啲人一早起身都冇行動冇方向</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins><br />\n早起身既唔只你，仲有班狗<br />\n覺得浪費個早上既你可以睇下有咩國際task做<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">上年黎明行動同罷工都叫成功，今次都一定得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins><br />\n無錯，係上年<br />\n今年已經係2020年，遊行集會唱個歌都重兵既地方<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">今日二讀一定要做向世界表達民意，一定要好似上年咁阻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins><br />\n唔一定要罷到工先表達到<br />\n再次重申，今年已經係2020，安全至上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>覺得今日可能阻唔到而又冇罷工行動好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></span> <br />\n想要啲行動感既你可以去做下國際任務<br />\n唔一定要每次都有實際行動先叫有交代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">我被罷工唔成，屌哂冇黎明行動既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins><br />\n你可以去返上一頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中午有活動<br />\n大家都一定係安全至上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a8fce7b5dfa1b37085b548ae7d87a14ae74a7d","tid":2037283,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:52:35.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be97072dd46fde5098aa1238c0a7291d93d00723","tid":2037283,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"[出定先] 聽日一定有班人話咩冇人出所以叫我地放棄<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fwKvCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fwKvCS</a>"},{"pid":"1f781dc103d76389d0f97f9dec7fcb1d36c6f75d","tid":2037283,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a9231ab3ef420b3094bafac659b87d6c7a6949","tid":2037283,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f2f7cab22388a5f5724ee7b9b5a0d29b4e8457","tid":2037283,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:04:02.000Z","msg":"Cant agree more"},{"pid":"5dfe940a4311902798b2f44c5b97a45974d3dec7","tid":2037283,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"開花都重狗？"},{"pid":"e5dc853bf9c0cdcac249543abb36880f360c22e6","tid":2037283,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:04:58.000Z","msg":"中午集氣啊"},{"pid":"b051e07e59f0ff83aa4179b1223ca9526ad44d2f","tid":2037283,"uid":97448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dfe940a4311902798b2f44c5b97a45974d3dec7","tid":2037283,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"開花都重狗？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"係未開花都重狗"},{"pid":"41ff3a0220edb379da2304556500a4b7396957db","tid":2037283,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"4d21e0cf8a3db2719787424ad1d900dfd61b9667","tid":2037283,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:05:18.000Z","msg":"唔講時間 地點 全部人咪on99咁<br />\n去支援d車都比人拉埋"},{"pid":"ad2f06795cd07fe418e7185b6e98ba18b87e50f2","tid":2037283,"uid":97448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0